To install GTK from the .tar included in this project, you need the following developpement libraries:

libglib2.0-dev
libatk1.0-dev
libsdl-pango-dev
libgdk-pixbuf2.0-dev
libxi-dev
libepoxy-dev
libatk-bridge2.0-dev

OR alternatively you can just install gtk with your package manager:
sudo apt-get install libgtk-3-dev
sudo dnf install gtk3-devel